name: Free Portfolio Template - Figma & Webflow Course
description:
This is the Project File for my Mega Web Design & Webflow Course for Beginners which is totally FREE.

With this course you can learn to Design your Portfolio from scratch in Figma and then build it in Webflow without using a single line of code. You can find the Figma Course on my YouTube Channel and the Webflow course on Skillshare.
